{
  "text": "The study incorporated qualitative methodology following COREQ guidelines [CITATION_1] . First, it followed a phenomenology study design as we aimed to explore stressors relevant to Pakistani context. We conducted serial in-depth interviews along with translating the tool and seeking expert's opinion [CITATION_2] . This was followed by community based scoring of each stressful item on the adapted tool (Fig. 1) .",
